messages:
Name: Alexandru Maxim
Nationality: Romania
Date of Birth: July 8, 1990
Position: Midfielder
Current club: Gaziantep FK
Süper Lig clubs played for: Gaziantep FK

Alexandru Maxim, the Gaziantep FK midfielder, has appeared in the vast majority of the team's Süper Lig games in 2020/2021, making 38 appearances overall and accumulating 3,045 minutes of playing time. He has been selected in the starting XI in all 38 of these appearances across their 40 fixtures.

Maxim last appeared in the league on May 11 for Gaziantep FK versus Rizespor. He netted a goal in that game for his team in their 5-4 loss. The midfielder has scored 15 Süper Lig goals this season, which is tied for the fifth most by a player in the competition in 2020/2021. He has amassed eight yellow cards.
A first league goal of the season for Maxim came against Göztepe in a 2-2 draw on September 26.
Maxim played 15 Süper Lig games last season for Gaziantep FK, scored seven goals and provided two assists.
Before moving to Gaziantep FK in August 2020, Maxim made 49 league appearances in total at Mainz 05, scoring three goals and providing two assists.
